# INSTALLATION

## Install the Plugin

1. Copy the Splitfile directory into:
    /Users/Admin/Library/Application Support/Sublime Text 2/Packages/

## Create Hotkeys

1. Open Sublime Text 2

2. Open menu: "Sublime Text 2" > Preferences > Key Bindings - User

3. Add (and customize) the following lines:
    { "keys": ["super+alt+ctrl+h"], "command": "splitfileh" },
    { "keys": ["super+alt+ctrl+v"], "command": "splitfilev" }


The entire file should look like this if you have no other custom keymappings:

[
    { "keys": ["super+alt+ctrl+h"], "command": "splitfileh" },
    { "keys": ["super+alt+ctrl+v"], "command": "splitfilev" }
]
